&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Land and validate Gift Cards.&lt;/strong&gt; Stand up the BD motion, partner economics, and product/lifecycle stack this channel needs. This is a new bet: your job is to move fast, find the right retail and distribution partners, test the model, and make a clear call on whether to scale or deprioritize within a defined timeframe.&lt;/li&gt;
