&lt;p&gt;As our Senior Localization Specialist focused on Language Quality &amp;amp; AI, you will own our strategy for evaluating language quality, as well as testing and training AI models to help us achieve quality at scale.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is a project-based role in which you will lead 1-3 major initiatives each quarter. Your work will directly support our global growth, requiring a blend of strategic thinking, creative problem-solving, and data-driven rigor to deliver measurable improvements.&lt;/p&gt;
